DRIVER PRIVACY POLICY

What Driver needs from you to function:
  - Your Google Drive account
  
What Drive gets from you:
  - Your email address

Does Driver share this information?
  - No.

Where are these collected information stored?
  - On-device. Driver only
  
Can Driver modify something?
  - No. Driver only has READ access to your Google Drive folder.
  
Why Driver needs them?
  - Driver uses Google Drive APIs in order to recieve Google Drive folder information (even if its a public Drive folder). This requires a Google account.
  
Questions? Feel free to reach out to lorandcompany (at) gmail (dot) com
